    "This formula specifies a comprehensive method for quantifying the net profit (or loss) obtained from the kth Bitcoin transaction, after considering the transaction fees.",
    "This way, the reward value at time-step t is equal to the value of PnL k (r t = PnL k).",
    "In describing the reward function, the second critical factor for an effective trading strategy is to maintain a low risk level.",
    "In this work, risk level is described as the percentage of the investment that the model is allowed to risk.",
    "After each decision made by the agent, the amount of investment is calculated, and if it is below a certain threshold, the agent receives a penalty."
